  <brief_title>Growth Hormone Treatment in Children Born Small for Gestational Age: Assessment of Satisfaction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Satisfaction With Growth Hormone Treatment in Children Born Small for Gestational Age: Benefits of Galenic Form of the Product</official_title>
