  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of this trial is to assess satisfaction with
      growth hormone treatment in children of both sexes born small for gestational age and who are
      receiving growth hormone treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
